review: One of my favorite places in TLV, this place shoulg get a michelin star!
Best coffee shop in Israel, I'm definitely recommending going there!
Such a nice place, you can get their breakfast, lunch and of course dinner.
If you look for junk food this is the place for you, the best burgers in Tel Aviv.
Probably among the few vegan places you can find in Haifa. The food is excellent and they don't just serve hummus there.
I was there once, a few dishes were missing but overall a cute place.
